<p>Who doesn't like "band camp?"  I have many fond memories of summer music camps as they gave me the opportunities to explore new places and play with extremely talented musicians.  I've been to Kansas City, Santa Barbara, Aspen, and the Island of Kauai as a participant in the International Institute of Young Musicians, Aspen Music Festival, and Prince Albert Music Festival.</p>

